      "body" : "Bitcoind contains no code for deleting your wallet, nor your bitcoind.conf file.\n\nIt could be unfortunate random disk corruption (check your system log for filesystem errors), but I agree with @jonasschnelli that disappearance of these two specific files is very suspicious and I\"d too recommend reinstalling the server, or hosting it somewhere else if you don't trust the hoster (mind that hot bitcoin wallets on VPS have been popular targets, e.g. the linode 'hacks').\n",
